      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. This car is in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and smells brand new! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it drives like a dream. I know I haven't sold much here yet, but I'm happy to chat, send more photos, or have you come by for a test drive so you can see how perfect it is for yourself. You won't find another one this clean!",
