    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional specimen that redefines the standard for 'pre-owned.' This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, showcasing a factory-fresh exterior with a deep, mirror-like finish and zero imperfections. Every panel gap is precise, and the paint remains entirely free of stone chips, swirls, or blemishes. Inside, the cabin retains its original showroom aroma; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no creases or wear, and the high-gloss trim pieces are devoid of even the finest micro-scratches. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It comes with a comprehensive, chronological folder of authorized service records, documenting every fluid change and inspection performed ahead of schedule. The engine bay is immaculate, and the undercarriage shows no signs of road debris or oxidation. All four alloy wheels are pristine, free of curb rash, and wrapped in high-performance tires with nearly full tread depth. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a collector-grade vehicle that looks, feels, and drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Includes all original keys, manuals, and a custom-fit car cover.",
      "price": 44900.0,
