      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you my absolute pride and joy. This car is in truly incredible condition\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this beauty since day one, keeping it sparkling clean and perfectly maintained. If you're looking for that 'new car' feel without the dealership price tag, you've found it. I'm happy to answer any questions or have you over to take a look, so just give me a shout!",
