    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Offering a concours-level 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine Carbon Black. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, boasting individual throttle bodies and a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. Mechanically flawless, the critical dual-VANOS system has been overhauled and rod bearings replaced with treated shells for total peace of mind. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission shifts with bolt-action precision, feeding power to a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis is equally sorted, featuring a reinforced rear subframe and a suspension geometry that remains tight and communicative. The paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the interior Nappa leather shows zero bolster wear. A turn-key investment for the purist who demands mechanical perfection.",
